title: POtHS - End Times - 69 - The Feasts of the Lord by Mark Biltz
description:
The Feasts of the Lord by Mark Biltz:
Speak unto the children of Israel, and say unto them. Concerning the feasts of YHWH, which ye shall proclaim to be holy convocations, even these are MY Feasts. Lev.23:2

The Spring Feasts were the Dress Rehersals for his First Coming to the Very Day.

Passover; Yeshua Died
Feast of Unleavened Bread; Yeshu was in the Grave 
Feast of First Fruits; Yeshua Rose
Feast of Pentecost; Ruach HaKodesh Poured Out

The Fall Feasts are the Dress Rehersals for his Second Coming to the very day.

Feast of Yom Teruah; Jacob's Trouble Begins
Feast of Yom Kippur; Israel calls upon Messiah
Feast of Tabernacles; Millennial Reign Begins

Also included in this download...
Signs - Part 49:
A compilation of various short clips presenting recent apocalyptic signs occurring around the world today and help us identify the state of affairs ushering the end of days.  View what's been happening in our time and descern for yourself the onset of Revelations and what may lay ahead.  

And various End Times video clips
